name: Trap-Jaw Hellgrammite
text: If this card is Special Summoned by the effect of a "Trap-Jaw" monster: You can add 1 "Trap-Jaw" Spell/Trap from your Deck to your hand. You can reveal 1 Insect monster in your hand; shuffle it back into the Deck and draw 1 card. You can only activate each effect of "Trap-Jaw Hellgrammite" once per turn.
